Package: govspeakr
Type: Package
Title: Convert standard markdown to govspeak markdown
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "best-practice-and-impact",
             email = "gsshelp@statistics.gov.uk"),
     person(given = "Sebastian",
            family = "Fox"),
     person(given = "David",
            family = "Foster"))
Description: Converts markdown scripts to a govspeak markdown
    that can be uploaded to the Whitehall publisher on the
    gov.uk website. For use in the development of
    Reproducible Analytical Pipelines (RAP).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/best-practice-and-impact/govspeakr
